symptoms: Grinding or squealing noise when applying the brakes
steering wheel vibration when brakes are applied
brakes sound like they are bad even when they are not.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unwanted emergency brake engagement can cause a sudden loss of control, leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also lead to a decrease in driver confidence and safety.
symptoms: Emergency brake engages making the vehicle stop short
parking brake becomes stuck and won't allow the vehicle to drive
car makes noises as if it's about to hit something even though there is nothing around
